# ARC Hardware Overview

- **Processor:** Raspberry Pi Zero 2 W (quad-core ARM Cortex-A53 @ 1 GHz)
- **RAM:** 512 MB LPDDR2 SDRAM
- **Storage:** microSD (up to 512GB)
- **Co-Processor:** RP2040 Pico (keyboard controller, QMK firmware)
- **Display:** 3.5" Waveshare TFT LCD, 480×320, resistive touch
- **Keyboard:** 40% custom QWERTY, RGB notification, tactile switches
- **Connectivity:** WiFi 802.11 b/g/n, Bluetooth 4.2 BLE, GSM (SIM800L), NFC (PN532), RF (CC1101, NRF24)
- **Audio:** I2S DAC, onboard speaker, 3.5mm headphone jack
- **Battery:** 3.7V Li-ion/LiPo, USB-C charging, MAX17048 fuel gauge
- **Power:** Soft-latching circuit, 5–8h runtime typical
- **Enclosure:** Custom PCB, 3D-printed case, ~140×75×28 mm

> Modular, portable, open source!
